rd":false,"selected":false,"Visible":true,"boundsInParent":"(0, 0 - 1080, 2037)","boundsInScreen":"(0, 225 - 1080, 2262)","children":[{"index":0,"class":"androidx.recyclerview.widget.RecyclerView","package":"com.zhihu.android","checkable":false,"checked":false,"clickable":false,"enabled":true,"focusable":true,"focused":false,"scrollable":true,"long-clickable":false,"password":false,"selected":false,"Visible":true,"boundsInParent":"(0, 0 - 1080, 2037)","boundsInScreen":"(0, 225 - 1080, 2260)","children":[{"index":0,"class":"androidx.appcompat.widget.LinearLayoutCompat","package":"com.zhihu.android","checkable":false,"checked":false,"clickable":true,"enabled":true,"focusable":true,"focused":false,"scrollable":false,"long-clickable":false,"password":false,"selected":false,"Visible":true,"boundsInParent":"(0, 0 - 492, 979)","boundsInScreen":"(33, 225 - 525, 1113)","children":[{"index":0,"text":"清朝皇帝的一天：看完你还想做皇帝吗？ | 在许多人眼里皇帝贵为九五之尊，过的应该是锦衣玉食、神仙般的生活。早上接受百官朝拜，晚上和妃子逍遥快活。但事实上清朝皇帝的一天到底是怎样的？虽清朝皇帝的作息稍有不同，但大致如下：每天凌晨4点天没亮皇帝就要起床上班了。如果皇帝没有按时起来，负责起床的太监会叫皇帝起床。随后太监会伺候皇帝洗漱换装。百善孝为先所以头等大事就是去向长辈请安，这时大约早上5点。比如康熙每天风雨无阻地去慈宁宫给奶奶孝庄请安以及去宁寿宫给母亲孝惠章皇太后请安。请安后便是早读时间，主要内容是记录前朝皇帝谕旨的《圣训》以及编年大记事《实录》。早读完就该去乾清门御门听政（早朝）了，此制度始于顺治，完善于康熙。时间为春夏上午6点，秋冬上午7点。康熙体恤官员便特谕延迟半个时辰。参与的官员有大学士、六部九卿等。整个过程包括：奏、听、议、决、行。康熙时几乎天天御门听政，自雍正后逐渐减少御门听政的频率。一来是御门听政参与人员众多保密性不够，二来是密折制度和军机处的建立给皇帝更好的选择。事务汇报完毕，大约早上8点，到了皇帝早膳时间。除吃饭外皇帝在这个时间会决定要召见哪些王公大臣，称为翻膳牌，红色代表王公，绿色代表大臣。早膳后已经将近9点，皇帝开始处理朝政，包括批阅奏折、召见大臣和下发谕旨。要处理的文件主要分为三类。题本：盖了官印的官方报告（难度大）；奏本：不盖官印的官方报告；奏折：皇帝与官员之间的私人通信，比如请安折（黄纸写）、非请安折（白纸写）处理了两个小时政务已经到了11点，上午的工作也告一段落。康熙此时会去弘德殿与老师们切磋学习，听经文讲解。结束后就到了晚膳时间，皇帝此时会决定晚上侍寝人选。晚膳后是娱乐时间。皇帝会去听戏、赏画、下棋、弹琴等。每个皇帝的爱好不同娱乐项目也不同。比如乾隆喜欢赏玩自己收藏的宝贝，道光则经常召集戏班在养心殿演戏。娱乐过后到了晚上6点，这时候皇帝也觉得肚子有点饿了，虽然已经过了两个正餐的时间，不过此时也可以传酒膳和吃点小点心。填饱肚子后，大约晚上7点，皇帝会前往坤宁宫开始礼佛祭神，这是自顺治入关后就定下的规矩。礼佛结束后差不多到了晚上8点，皇帝就准备沐浴就寝了。清宫规定，只有幼年皇帝大婚典礼后，皇帝夫妇才能在坤宁宫东暖阁洞房共居三天，其他时间都必须各住自己寝宫。皇帝平时不能在嫔妃宫里过夜，侍寝时会把她们召到自己宫中，但也不能整夜共寝，只能在寝宫旁围房暂住。皇帝入睡时，仅随侍太监能留在身边。 #一图读懂# #每日知识图#","resource-id":"com.zhihu.android:id\/content","class":"android.widget.TextView","package":"com.zhihu.android","checkable":false,"checked":false,"clickable":false,"enabled":true,"focusable":false,"focused":false,"scrollable":false,"long-clickable":false,"password":false,"selected":false,"Visible":true,"boundsInParent":"(0, 0 - 426, 108)","boundsInScreen":"(66, 817 - 492, 925)"},{"index":1,"class":"androidx.appcompat.widget.LinearLayoutCompat","package":"com.zhihu.android","checkable":false,"checked":false,"clickable":false,"enabled":true,"focusable":false,"focused":false,"scrollable":false,"long-clickable":false,"password":false,"selected":false,"Visible":true,"boundsInParent":"(0, 0 - 492, 106)","boundsInScreen":"(33, 925 - 525, 1031)","children":[{"index":0,"text":"不简单的历史","resource-id":"com.zhihu.android:id\/mPublishNameView","class":"android.widget.TextView","package":"com.zhihu.android","checkable":false,"checked":false,"clickable":false,"enabled":true,"focusable":false,"focused":false,"scrollable":false,"long-clickable":false,"password":false,"selected":false,"Visible":true,"boundsInParent":"(0, 0 - 198, 45)","boundsInScreen":"(127, 955 - 325, 1000)"},{"index":1,"resource-id":"com.zhihu.android:id\/mApplaudLayout","class":"androidx.appcompat.widget.LinearLayoutCompat","package":"com.zhihu.android","checkable":false,"checked":false,"clickable":true,"enabled":true,"focusable":true,"focused":false,"scrollable":false,"long-clickable":false,"password":false,"selected":false,"Visible":true,"boundsInParent":"(0, 0 - 136, 50)","boundsInScreen":"(389, 953 - 525, 1003)","children":[{"index":0,"text":"211","resource-id":"com.zhihu.android:id\/mApplaudCountView","class":"android.widget.TextView","package":"com.zhihu.android","checkable":false,"checked":false,"clickable":false,"enabled":true,"focusable":false,"focused":false,"scrollable":false,"long-clickable":false,"password":false,"selected":false,"Visible":true,"boundsInParent":"(0, 0 - 45, 45)","boundsInScreen":"(447, 955 - 492, 1000)"}]}]},{"index":2,"text":"每日知识图","class":"android.widget.TextView","package":"com.zhihu.android","checkable":false,"checked":false,"clickable":false,"enabled":true,"focusable":false,"focused":false,"scrollable":false,"long-clickable":false,"password":false,"selected":false,"Visible":true,"boundsInParent":"(0, 0 - 168, 37)","boundsInScreen":"(77, 1037 - 245, 1074)"},{"index":3,"text":"一图读懂","class":"android.widget.TextView","package":"com.zhihu.android","checkable":false,"checked":false,"clickable":false,"enabled":true,"focusable":false,"focused":false,"scrollable":false,"long-clickable":false,"password":false,"selected":false,"Visible":true,"boundsInParent":"(0, 0 - 141, 37)","boundsInScreen":"(283, 1037 - 424, 1074)"}]},{"index":1,"class":"androidx.appcompat.widget.LinearLayoutCompat","package":"com.zhihu.android","checkable":false,"checked":false,"clickable":true,"enabled":true,"focusable":true,"focused":false,"scrollable":false,"long-clickable":false,"password":false,"selected":false,"Visible":true,"boundsInParent":"(0, 0 - 492, 979)","boundsInScreen":"(555, 225 - 1047, 705)","children":[{"index":0,"text":"空心菜｜怎样炒出绿油油、不发黑的空心菜？ | 🥬🥬🥬空心菜上市有一段时间了。前两天在厨房捣鼓实验时，听到阿姨犯难嘀咕：空心菜怎么炒才会绿油油的、不易变色？在阿姨为绿色苦恼的时候，我却在窃喜，选题这不就来了！-很多教程给炝炒空心菜总结的要点是：火力大，速度快。我们以火力为变量，分别用大、中、小三种火力炒空心菜，另设一组增加焯水的步骤；来看不同火力炒出的空心菜，在颜色上是否有差别。-👉🏻实验结果加热时间：小火>中火>大火>焯水大火。炒出时绿色：小火<中火≈大火<焯水大火。小火组是偏暗的橄榄绿，中火组和大火组是偏黄的亮绿色，差别不大；焯水大火组是青绿色，在四组中颜色蕞绿（图3）放置10分钟：小火组和中火组多数菜梗变为褐色，大火及焯水大火组有少量变色，颜色相对较绿（图4）。完全变色时间：小火约10min，中火约30min，大火约60min，焯水大火约120min（图5）。-⭕️加热时间越短，空心菜越绿，且维持时间越长；但久置后或多或少都会变色。-👉🏻实验原理-✔️为什么绿色蔬菜会变色？我们都知道植物的绿色来自叶绿素，绿叶蔬菜变色，本质是叶绿素在变化。-叶绿素的分子结构很可爱，由四个吡咯环组成一个大环脑袋（卟啉环），中间嵌着一个镁离子；脑袋后挂着一条植醇尾，旁边还有一个乙酰基。其中镁是叶绿素呈现鲜亮绿色的关键之一，但它非常脆弱，遇到高温或酸就会脱离。-烹饪时，叶绿素受热失去镁离子，成为脱镁叶绿素，呈现黯淡的橄榄绿色；比橄榄色更严重的是褐色，那是脱镁叶绿素进一步失去乙酰基后形成的焦脱镁叶绿素。这就是蔬菜逐渐发黄暗沉变黑的过程。-另外，植物细胞内还存在叶绿素酶，当它和叶绿素相遇时，会断开植醇尾连接大环脑袋的酯键，使叶绿素更易变色（图8）。-✔️如何防止\/延缓绿色蔬菜变色？①“大火快炒”。这是为了不让叶绿素因长时间受热而发生变色，既能让绿叶菜断生又能保持翠绿。然而若是没有经过大量练习，恐怕很难做到既快且熟，难免出现夹生的情况。-②增加汆烫\/焯水的步骤。这也是另设焯水大火组的原因。叶绿素酶的活性在66-77℃之间达到顶点，超过90℃会完全失活。焯水一方面使叶绿素酶在高温下失活，保护叶绿素；另一方面使蔬菜受热均匀，后续快炒时防止夹生。焯水时间不宜过长，视蔬菜的量控制在1-2分钟之内即可。-③注意余温。许多老一辈会在炒好装盘的青菜中间掏个洞（图7），目的是为了散热，因为余温足以将菜闷黄。同理，蔬菜汆烫后要迅速投入冰水降温，这样做还能让蔬菜更脆。 #每日知识图# #一图读懂#","resource-id":"com.zhihu.android:id\/content","class":"android.widget.TextView","package":"com.zhihu.android","checkable":false,"checked":false,"clickable":false,"enabled":true,"focusable":false,"focused":false,"scrollable":false,"long-clickable":false,"password":false,"selected":false,"Visible":true,"boundsInParent":"(0, 0 - 426, 108)","boundsInScreen":"(588, 409 - 1014, 517)"},{"index":1,"class":"androidx.appcompat.widget.LinearLayoutCompat","package":"com.zhihu.android","checkable":false,"checked":false,"clickable":false,"enabled":true,"focusable":false,"focused":false,"scrollable":false,"long-clickable":false,"password":false,"selected":false,"Visible":true,"boundsInParent":"(0, 0 - 492, 106)","boundsInScreen":"(555, 517 - 1047, 623)","children":[{"index":0,"text":"南食召lab","resource-id":"com.zhihu.android:id\/mPublishNameView","class":"android.widget.TextView","package":"com.zhihu.android","checkable":false,"checked":false,"clickable":false,"enabled":true,"focusable":false,"focused":false,"scrollable":false,"long-clickable":false,"password":false,"selected":false,"Visible":true,"boundsInParent":"(0, 0 - 145, 45)","boundsInScreen":"(649, 547 - 794, 592)"},{"index":1,"resource-id":"com.zhihu.android:id\/mApplaudLayout","class":"androidx.appcompat.widget.LinearLayoutCompat","package":"com.zhihu.android","checkable":false,"checked":false,"clickable":true,"enabled":true,"focusable":true,"focused":false,"scrollable":false,"long-clickable":false,"password":false,"selected":false,"Visible":true,"boundsInParent":"(0, 0 - 137, 50)","boundsInScreen":"(910, 545 - 1047, 595)","children":[{"index":0,"text":"114","resource-id":"com.zhihu.android:id\/mApplaudCountView","class":"android.widget.TextView","package":"com.zhihu.android","checkable":false,"checked":false,"clickable":false,"enabled":true,"focusable":false,"focused":false,"scrollable":false,"long-clickable":false,"password":false,"selected":false,"Visible":true,"boundsInParent":"(0, 0 - 46, 45)","boundsInScreen":"(968, 547 - 1014, 592)"}]}]},{"index":2,"text":"想法精选","class":"android.widget.TextView","package":"com.zhihu.android","checkable":false,"checked":false,"clickable":false,"enabled":true,"focusable":false,"focused":false,"scrollable":false,"long-clickable":false,"password":false,"selected":false,"Visible":true,"boundsInParent":"(0, 0 - 108, 37)","boundsInScreen":"(599, 629 - 707, 666)"}]},{"index":2,"class":"androidx.appcompat.widget.LinearLayoutCompat","package":"com.zhihu.android","checkable":false,"checked":false,"clickable":true,"enabled":true,"focusable":true,"focused":false,"scrollable":false,"long-clickable":false,"password":false,"selected":false,"Visible":true,"boundsInParent":"(0, 0 - 492, 897)","boundsInScreen":"(33, 1146 - 525, 2043)","children":[{"index":0,"text":"你看 ai作画渲染后 蜘蛛侠都变得那么科技感 赛博朋克十足🤔","resource-id":"com.zhihu.android:id\/content","class":"android.widget.TextView","package":"com.zhihu.android","checkable":false,"checked":false,"clickable":false,"enabled":true,"focusable":false,"focused":false,"scrollable":false,"long-clickable":false,"password":false,"selected":false,"Visible":true,"boundsInParent":"(0, 0 - 426, 108)","boundsInScreen":"(66, 1829 - 492, 1937)"},{"index":1,"class":"androidx.appcompat.widget.LinearLayoutCompat","package":"com.zhihu.android","checkable":false,"checked":false,"clickable":false,"enabled":true,"focusable":false,"focused":false,"scrollable":false,"long-clickable":false,"password":false,"selected":false,"Visible":true,"boundsInParent":"(0, 0 - 492, 106)","boundsInScreen":"(33, 1937 - 525, 2043)","children":[{"index":0,"text":"朱尔的胖","resource-id":"com.zhihu.android:id\/mPublishNameView","class":"android.widget.TextView","package":"com.zhihu.android","checkable":false,"checked":false,"clickable":false,"enabled":true,"focusable":false,"focused":false,"scrollable":false,"long-clickable":false,"password":false,"selected":false,"Visible":true,"boundsInParent":"(0, 0 - 132, 45)","boundsInScreen":"(127, 1967 - 259, 2012)"},{"index":1,"resource-id":"com.zhihu.android:id\/mApplaudLayout","class":"androidx.appcompat.widget.LinearLayoutCompat","package":"com.zhihu.android","checkable":false,"checked":false,"clickable":true,"enabled":true,"focusable":true,"focused":false,"scrollable":false,"long-clickable":false,"password":false,"selected":false,"Visible":true,"boundsInParent":"(0, 0 - 131, 50)","boundsInScreen":"(394, 1965 - 525, 2015)","children":[{"index":0,"text":"43","resource-id":"com.zhihu.android:id\/mApplaudCountView","class":"android.widget.TextView","package":"com.zhihu.android","checkable":false,"checked":false,"clickable":false,"enabled":true,"focusable":false,"focused":false,"scrollable":false,"long-clickable":false,"password":false,"selected":false,"Visible":true,"boundsInParent":"(0, 0 - 40, 45)","boundsInScreen":"(452, 1967 - 492, 2012)"}]}]}]},{"index":3,"class":"androidx.appcompat.widget.LinearLayoutCompat","package":"com.zhihu.android","checkable":false,"checked":false,"clickable":true,"enabled":true,"focusable":true,"focused":false,"scrollable":false,"long-clickable":false,"password":false,"selected":false,"Visible":true,"boundsInParent":"(0, 0 - 492, 979)","boundsInScreen":"(555, 738 - 1047, 1717)","children":[{"index":0,"text":"拒绝7种伤胃早餐❗️附孩子营养早餐搭配公式|||早餐是孩子一天当中相当重要的一顿饭，孩子早餐吃的好不仅一个上午精神饱满，还对身体健康有益。但有些我们看似习以为常经常吃的早餐，其实对孩子是有害无益的，这里给大家总结了7种最伤孩子的早餐，家长们要注意了1、白粥+馒头2、隔夜饭+榨菜3、豆浆+油条4、半熟的糖心蛋5、腌制食品（腊肉、咸鱼、咸鸭蛋、咸菜、酸菜）6、早餐奶7、烤肠、香肠、培根另外还给大家整理了营养早餐万能搭配公式，给孩子准备的早餐至少要包含这三种营养元素：碳水化物+蛋白质+膳食纤维。像儿子上小学后早上时间紧，但为了保证早餐的营养，我会给他准备拉面说番茄浓汤拉面，配料很齐，5分钟就搞定了，并且里面包含的营养很全面，像早餐所需的碳水、蛋白质、膳食纤维都有拉面说是非油炸的鲜面，含有丰富的碳水化合物，能够提供身体所需的能量。维生素：汤底由新鲜番茄熬制，肉酱包里也有新鲜番茄块和玉米，含有大量维生素C，整盒相当于摄入了一颗半番茄蛋白质：肉酱包有大颗粒的肉搭配玉米颗粒，含有丰富的蛋白质、矿物质和维生素，荤素搭配，营养均衡膳食纤维：拉面里还添加了小麦麸皮，还有肉酱包里的玉米也含有膳食纤维，助于肠道健康微量元素：有肉有菜，含有丰富的铁、锌、镁、维生素等微量元素另外我再给他搭配鸡蛋、牛奶和坚果，一上午的营养得到了保证。有时儿子早上起来没有胃口，但他喜欢吃这个拉面，酸酸甜甜的味道，汤底加了番茄和香草黄油酱熬煮，香而不腻，很开胃。这个配料也干净，不添加防腐剂和人工色素，给孩子吃也放心。#想法打卡挑战赛第6期# # # 儿童营养早餐#","resource-id":"com.zhihu.android:id\/content","class":"android.widget.TextView","package":"com.zhihu.android","checkable":false,"checked":false,"clickable":false,"enabled":true,"focusable":false,"focused":false,"scrollable":false,"long-clickable":false,"password":false,"selected":false,"Visible":true,"boundsInParent":"(0, 0 - 426, 108)","boundsInScreen":"(588, 1421 - 1014, 1529)"},{"index":1,"class":"androidx.appcompat.widget.LinearLayoutCompat","package":"com.zhihu.android","checkable":false,"checked":false,"clickable":false,"enabled":true,"focusable":false,"focused":false,"scrollable":false,"long-clickable":false,"password":false,"selected":false,"Visible":true,"boundsInParent":"(0, 0 - 492, 106)","boundsInScreen":"(555, 1529 - 1047, 1635)","children":[{"index":0,"text":"北斗精神力量","resource-id":"com.zhihu.android:id\/mPublishNameView","class":"android.widget.TextView","package":"com.zhihu.android","checkable":false,"checked":false,"clickable":false,"enabled":true,"focusable":false,"focused":false,"scrollable":false,"long-clickable":false,"password":false,"selected":false,"Visible":true,"boundsInParent":"(0, 0 - 198, 45)","boundsInScreen":"(649, 1559 - 847, 1604)"},{"index":1,"resource-id":"com.zhihu.android:id\/mApplaudLayout","class":"androidx.appcompat.widget.LinearLayoutCompat","package":"com.zhihu.android","checkable":false,"checked":false,"clickable":true,"enabled":true,"focusable":true,"focused":false,"scrollable":false,"long-clickable":false,"password":false,"selected":false,"Visible":true,"boundsInParent":"(0, 0 - 151, 50)","boundsInScreen":"(896, 1557 - 1047, 1607)","children":[{"index":0,"text":"258","resource-id":"com.zhihu.android:id\/mApplaudCountView","class":"android.widget.TextView","package":"com.zhihu.android","checkable":false,"checked":false,"clickable":false,"enabled":true,"focusable":false,"focused":false,"scrollable":false,"long-clickable":false,"password":false,"selected":false,"Visible":true,"boundsInP